msgstr "Рассчитать стоимость доставки"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:154
msgid ""
"Shipping cost is the :guilabel:`Delivery cost` specified in the rule that "
"satisfies the :guilabel:`Condition`, plus any extra charges from "
"the :guilabel:`Margin on rate` and :guilabel:`Additional margin`."
msgstr ""
"Стоимость доставки — это :guilabel:`Стоимость доставки`, указанная в "
"правиле, которое соответствует :guilabel:`Условию`, плюс любые "
"дополнительные сборы из :guilabel:`Наценки на тариф` "
"и :guilabel:`Дополнительной наценки`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:158
msgid ""
"Total = Rule's~Delivery~Cost + (Margin~on~rate \\times Rule's~Delivery~Cost) "
"+ Additional~margin\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Итого = Стоимость~доставки~правила + (Наценка~на~тариф \\times "
"Стоимость~доставки~правила) + Дополнительная~наценка\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:162
msgid "With the two following rules set up:"
msgstr "При настройке следующих двух правил:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:164
msgid "If the order contains five or fewer products, shipping is $20"
msgstr "Если заказ содержит пять или меньше товаров, доставка стоит $20"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:165
msgid "If the order contains more than five products, shipping is $50."
msgstr "Если заказ содержит более пяти товаров, доставка стоит $50."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Margin on Rate` is `10%` and :guilabel:`Additional margin` is "
"`$9.00`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Наценка на тариф` составляет `10%`, а :guilabel:`Дополнительная "
"наценка` — `$9,00`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:None
msgid ""
"Show example of \"Based on rules\" shipping method with margins configured."
msgstr ""
"Показать пример способа доставки «На основе правил» с настроенными наценками."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:172
msgid ""
"When the first rule is applied, the delivery cost is $31 (20 + (0.1 * 20) + "
"9). When the second rule is applied, the delivery cost is $64 (50 + (0.1 * "
"50) + 9)."
msgstr ""
"Когда применяется первое правило, стоимость доставки составляет $31 (20 + "
