"Route setting which enables a product to resupplied from a second warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Настройка маршрута, которая позволяет пополнять продукт со второго склада."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:104
