msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Дата`: группирует записи "
"по :guilabel:`Год`, :guilabel:`Квартал`, :guilabel:`Месяц`, :guilabel:`Неделя` "
"или :guilabel:`День`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/moves_history.rst:79
msgid ""
