#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:94
msgid ""
"Verify that each product in the catalog is configured with the chosen vendor "
"and that the Purchase Order is in the |RFQ| stage"
msgstr ""
"Убедитесь, что каждый товар в каталоге настроен с выбранным поставщиком и "
"что заказ на закупку находится на стадии |RFQ|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:98
msgid ""
"By default, products listed in the product catalog are filtered by vendor."
msgstr ""
"По умолчанию продукты, перечисленные в каталоге продуктов, фильтруются по "
"поставщику."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/suggest.rst:100
msgid ""
"Remove the filter in the search bar to view all items or use the built-"
