#~ msgid ""
#~ "By default, Odoo has a 50 milliseconds delay between each successive scan "
#~ "(it helps avoid accidental double scanning). If you want to suppress this "
#~ "delay, you can configure your scanner to insert a carriage return at the "
#~ "end of each barcode. This is usually the default configuration and can be "
#~ "explicitly configured by scanning a specific barcode in the user manual "
#~ "('CR suffix ON', 'Apply Enter for suffix', etc.)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "По умолчанию Odoo имеет задержку 50 миллисекунд между каждым последующим "
